#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.53"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.53:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.53:0.2"
msgid "6. Sākacchavagga"
msgstr "6. Discussion"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.53:0.3"
msgid "53. Aggisutta"
msgstr "53. Fire"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.112"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.53:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya "
"sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pavisiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"Then several mendicants robed up in the morning and, taking their bowls and "
"robes, entered Sāvatthī for alms."

msgctxt "sn46.53:1.2"
msgid "(Pariyāyasuttasadisaṃ.)"
msgstr "(The same as the previous discourse.)"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.53:2.1"
msgid "“Evaṃvādino, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evamassu vacanīyā:"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when wanderers who follow other paths say this, you should say "
"to them:"

msgctxt "sn46.53:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘yasmiṃ, āvuso, samaye līnaṃ cittaṃ hoti, katamesaṃ tasmiṃ samaye "
"bojjhaṅgānaṃ akālo bhāvanāya, katamesaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bojjhaṅgānaṃ kālo "
"bhāvanāya?"
msgstr ""
"‘Reverends, which awakening factors should not be developed when the mind is "
"sluggish? And which awakening factors should be developed at that time?"

msgctxt "sn46.53:2.3"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ panāvuso, samaye uddhataṃ cittaṃ hoti, katamesaṃ tasmiṃ samaye "
"bojjhaṅgānaṃ akālo bhāvanāya, katamesaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bojjhaṅgānaṃ kālo "
"bhāvanāyā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which awakening factors should not be developed when the mind is restless? "
"And which awakening factors should be developed at that time?’"

msgctxt "sn46.53:2.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ puṭṭhā, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā na ceva sampāyissanti, "
"uttariñca vighātaṃ āpajjissanti."
msgstr ""
"Questioned like this, the wanderers who follow other paths would be stumped, "
"and, in addition, would get frustrated."

msgctxt "sn46.53:2.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn46.53:2.6"
msgid "Yathā taṃ, bhikkhave, avisayasmiṃ."
msgstr "Because they’re out of their element."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.53:3.1"
msgid ""
"Nāhaṃ taṃ, bhikkhave, passāmi sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake "
"sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya yo imesaṃ pañhānaṃ veyyākaraṇena "
"cittaṃ ārādheyya, aññatra tathāgatena vā tathāgatasāvakena vā ito vā pana "
"sutvā."
msgstr ""
"I don’t see anyone in this world—with its gods, Māras, and Brahmās, this "
"population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans—who could "
"provide a satisfying answer to these questions except for the Realized One "
"or his disciple or someone who has heard it from them."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.53:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, bhikkhave, samaye līnaṃ cittaṃ hoti, akālo tasmiṃ samaye "
"passaddhisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya, akālo samādhisambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya, "
"akālo upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa bhāvanāya."
msgstr ""
"When the mind is sluggish, it’s the wrong time to develop the awakening "
"factors of tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.53:4.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn46.53:4.3"
msgid "Līnaṃ, bhikkhave, cittaṃ taṃ etehi dhammehi dussamuṭṭhāpayaṃ hoti."
msgstr "Because it’s hard to stimulate a sluggish mind with these things."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.113"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.53:5.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso parittaṃ aggiṃ ujjāletukāmo assa."
msgstr "Suppose someone wanted to make a small fire flare up."

msgctxt "sn46.53:5.2"
msgid ""
"So tattha allāni ceva tiṇāni pakkhipeyya, allāni ca gomayāni pakkhipeyya, "
"allāni ca kaṭṭhāni pakkhipeyya, udakavātañca dadeyya, paṃsukena ca okireyya;"
msgstr ""
"If they toss wet grass, cow-dung, and timber on it, spray it with water, and "
"scatter dirt on it,"

msgctxt "sn46.53:5.3"
msgid "bhabbo nu kho so puriso parittaṃ aggiṃ ujjāletun”ti?"
msgstr "could they make it flare up?”"

msgctxt "sn46.53:5.4"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“No, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
